## Research Use and Attribution

When using this code or data for research purposes, please cite the associated 
publication and acknowledge the use of AI assistance in development as documented 
in DEVELOPMENT_NOTES.md.

## Data Usage Terms

The head nod data included in this repository is provided for research purposes.
Users should respect participant privacy and follow ethical guidelines for 
research data usage. The data should not be used for commercial purposes without 
explicit permission from the original data collectors.
